The regulatory environment also plays a significant role in shaping the CNS stimulants market. Strict regulations governing the approval and commercialization of CNS medications ensure that only safe and effective products reach the market. Market players must adhere to regulatory standards and demonstrate the quality, safety, and efficacy of their CNS stimulants through rigorous clinical trials and regulatory submissions.

